{"tid":352359,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【食人扶手梯】當跑步機逆行狂奔 東莞女仆低夾手指","createTime":"2017-08-08T17:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T18:23:43.000Z","uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"628d79366a835a213d90a08c06eada95b91b73ad","tid":352359,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"使用扶手電梯時要正確，否則隨時會發生意外！東莞塘廈一個商場的女售貨員，近日將下行扶手電梯當成跑步機，逆向狂奔，未料失足跌倒，手指被卡在梯級縫隙間。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周二（1日）晚，影片顯示這名穿着紅色上衣、深藍色裙子的女售貨員，在一部向下的扶手電梯前準備，然後使勁往上跑，可是她只跑了三級樓梯，便疑是失去平衡跌倒，這時她右手握着扶手，跌坐在梯級上，左手手指被卡在梯級縫隙中。<br />\n<br />\n附近的店員和民眾見狀，有人按下緊急停止鍵，扶手電梯停止移動，大批民眾上前幫助女店員，女店員只是受了輕傷。　<br />\n<br />\n商場的管理員稱，其實之前受傷女店員與同事已在扶手電梯上玩了好幾分鐘，她們將它當成跑步機，不斷逆向上行，傷者是準備一口氣跑上樓時，疑一腳踏空，跌倒在梯級上。<br />\n<br />\n有網民看過片段後分析，這名跌倒的女售貨員疑是在扶手電梯上抽筯，才會失平衡跌倒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170808&amp;guid=57053556&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170808%26guid%3D57053556%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=7l2NxX2U2C0wnsvbV6UrZjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=e716f24e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170808%26guid%3D57053556%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=067751ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170808&amp;guid=57053556&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"cce827e8145dbf7507626ecccd683d8e47871f26","tid":352359,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"成日都有人玩出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wmrot25c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwmrot25c&h=c1bfae87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df8ebbca656e3ac658747feb096a32dabd4b3758","tid":352359,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"向後行 有MJ歌聽"},{"pid":"a3e0768b31756befb63d07b6348b0e252b88ed71","tid":352359,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a31160381be789e16d1443dd40a7d3e970e96c","tid":352359,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"921a479a5a2b0030d5533b9dcafcc5032c07d5b9","tid":352359,"uid":17081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都有人玩出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wmrot25c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwmrot25c&h=c1bfae87&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/fe/H8E3.gif/revision/latest?cb20130825181309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ffe%2FH8E3.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb20130825181309&h=a7f8ce7f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}